{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, during the course of work, I kept on going every morning and came back in the evening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we tried to run around from one block to the other block, until I found my two brothers there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Who, in turn, told me that my sister is also someplace in a camp, there, that they found out from-- from somebody.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we ended up being, now, four of us in the same place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't see our sister for a while, till later on we did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But now, we tried to get so the three brothers together that we all kept in the same block, if we could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't so easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at least we tried to go to the same work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when one fell down-- fell down, two of them were lifting up the-- the third one who couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there, food was, I mean-- it was unavailable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the segment of the population that the Russians that were captured-- they were really Ukraines-- in the-- in the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans were very cunning and smart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew exactly what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took the people-- Ukraines are-- are Jew-haters, I would say-- on top of list.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They take them, they gave them all the details in Birkenau that have something to do with food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put them in charge of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They put them in charge of the latrines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put them in every kind of a place where they could do with the Jewish population whatever they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, of course, they would come in the morning, bring you the coffee-- which was supposed to be coffee or tea-- in-- in a barrel, in an open barrel.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
